About PinkCoin

PinkCoin (PINK) is a cryptocurrency. Users are able to generate PINK through the process of mining. PinkCoin has a current supply of 429,658,349 PINK with 404,397,913 PINK in circulation. The last known price of PinkCoin is 0.002402 USD and is down 4.29% over the last 24 hours. It is currently trading on 3 active market(s) with 811 USD traded over the last 24 hours. More information can be found at http://getstarted.with.pink/.
